flowchart LR
  classDef sync fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:2px
  classDef rt fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px

  L[loader.ts<br/>sync ~5KB inline]
  L --> Q[queue stub<br/>window._testa]
  L --> MP[history monkey-patch<br/>idempotent]

  R[runtime/index.ts<br/>defer ~30-40KB]
  R --> CK[cookies.ts]
  R --> CN[consent.ts]
  R --> NW[network/<br/>outbox + transport + health]
  R --> RU[rules/<br/>audience + custom-js]
  R --> EX[experiments/<br/>traffic + apply + redirect]
  R --> LG[legacy.ts<br/>window.Analytica.*]
  R --> SP[spa.ts<br/>route-change handler]

  Q -. drained by .-> R
  MP -. _testa:locationchange .-> SP
  SP -. re-runs cycle .-> R

  class L,Q,MP sync
  class R,CK,CN,NW,RU,EX,LG,SP rt
